HEADWORD: Scapulet
<hw>Scap"u*let</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Dim. of
<ets>scapula</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A secondary mouth
